README
=======
Myparish is an application that helps, maintain baptism and marriage certificates of a parish;


Features planed:
=================
	1. Add/Remove/Modify/Print Birth certificates;
	2. Add/remove/Modify/Print Marriage certificates; 
	3. Search both Marriage and Birth certificates;
	4. Interface to set global defautls like,Parish name,Pin and Parish priest name,etc.

Compiling:
==========
You may need gtk+ and sqlite development headers to compile this application.

To compile the code navigate inside the directory parish_management_system  in terminal and execute the following command:
   'make'

Running the application:
========================
After compiling the code run the application using the following command:
    './parish'

